results.title: TBOTV:A Gathering of Fear, Part 3
results.description: D'Spayre relates his encounters with the Earth to the other Fear Lords and begins his outline for The Great Fear.

results.title: Is There a Doctor Not In The House?
results.description: The Doctors, Strange and Druid, head for Tibet to help the other Doctor, Doom, be reconstituted.  An ultimate good Doom is created and tries to make sure the regular/evil Dr. Doom stays inert forever.

results.title: To Hela and Back
results.description: Doc, Clea, and Scarlet Witch succeed in reviving Thor.  Meanwhile Rintrah and Pip go off to join Firelord and Drax who are trapped in the Jurassic period.

results.title: Footnote to Infinity [Infinity Gauntlet crossover]
results.description: Adam Warlock now wears the Infinity Gauntlet and its power is almost too much for him.  Doc gets to use each of his old standby artifacts to counteract the Gauntlet's effects.

results.title: Frankensurfer
results.description: The history of the Frankenstein's followed by a battle with the Frankensurfer.

results.title: The Fury of the Fear Lords - The Great Fear Part 1 of 3
Fear Itself  [The Great Fear, Part 1 of 3]
results.description: Doc and Clea team up to fight Nightmare (who flees), and then the Lurker Unknown who they defeat.

results.title: The Fear That Kills [The Great Fear, Part 2 of 3]
results.description: Doc and crew are simultaneously attacked by Nox and her two sons, Phobos and Deimos, and the Fear Eaters, but it appears the minor Fear Lords defeat is all a part of the master plan of Dweller in the Darkness.

results.title: Fight to the Finish with the DRAGON!
Dragon's Dream
results.description: Doc and the New Defenders (now called the Dragoncircle) fight the Dragon of the Moon.

results.title: The Fearsome Conclusion - The Great Fear Part 3 of 3
From Hope and Fear Set Free... [The Great Fear, Part 3 of 3]
results.description: After defeating Doc, the remaining Fear Lords battle over who is going to be the top dog.  But Doc managers to get a Sending off to the Man Without Fear, Daredevil.

results.title: A Wolverine at the Door
results.description: Wolverine is possessed by the Undying Ones and attacks Doc and Clea in bed.  Next Doc and Wolverine go to the dimension of the Undying One thru a Sa'arpool to stop them once and for all.

results.title: Galactus, Go Home!
results.description: Galactus comes calling on Doctor Strange, and commands Doc to accompany him to discovery why Eternity is in a trance in deep space.

results.title: Caught in the Eye of the Storm [Infinity War Crossover]
An Eye for an Eye [Infinity War Crossover]
results.description: Agamotto gets ticked off that Galactus wants to use his precious Eye and takes it back from Doc.  A battle between Agamotto and Galactus ensues, but who will win?

results.title: The Color Crimson [Infinity War Crossover]
results.description: While traveling to the source of Eternity's defeat, Cyttorak grabs Doc and Nova to be his High Priest and Priestess.  So Doc summons Juggernaut to help him out.

results.title: Death's Greatest Hits
results.description: When Galactus' ship is disintegrated, Doc again meets Death who takes him on a tour of the deaths of all of his family members.

results.title: Behold the Strange Bedfellows--the Most Magical Team-Up of All Time
Strange Bedfellows
results.description: Doc and the other Mystic heavyweights try to free the Earth from it paralysis, only to encounter the Masked Dr. Strange.

results.title: Will the Real Dr. Strange Please Stand Up?
Strange Bedfellows II
results.description: Doctor Strange has to battle with his Masked self from Counter Earth and his Magus created Doppleganger self.

results.title: To Serve in Heaven
results.description: Clea deposes Umar and Baron Mordo, only to unleash Dormammu.  Meanwhile Doc has to call upon the Vishanti to save him from destruction, and they demand he accompany them for a 5000 year war.

results.title: The Wrath of Gods
results.description: We get to see a manifestation of every major entity Doc has called upon in his career.  Each wants him to fight in the War of Seven Spheres, but he says NO and loses any chance to invoke their power.

results.title: 7ouled Out [The Faust Gambit Part I]
results.description: After Rintrah asks to be Doc's apprentice, Baron Mordo shows up and nearly succeeds in stealing Doc's soul.  Doc reverses the spell and traps Mordo and the kidnapped Sara Wolfe in a tiny soul sphere.

results.title: An Unabashedly Personal Remembrance
results.description: Thomas gives us some informative back history about his part in Doc's origins and inspirations.

results.title: Guest Starring: Ghost Rider! Hulk! Silver Surfer!
The Heart of Darkness
results.description: Doc recruits a new group of Secret Defenders to shore up his loss of power and fight Dormammu in the Dark Dimension.

results.title: Redemption
results.description: Rintrah goes out for a walk and discovers a cult powered by a ancient being.

results.title: Field of Bad Dreams
results.description: Nightmare has taken control of Morbius as a trap for Doc, and when Doc comes looking for Morbius, the trap works and Nightmare takes over Doc's physical body.

results.title: Nightmare on Bleecker Street
results.description: Nightmare physically enters our dimension by taking control of Doc's body.  Morbius is freed and he and Nightmare (in Doc's body) duke it out.

results.title: Dr. Strange Dares to Challenge -- Eternity
From Here...To There...To Eternity
results.description: Doc calls upon the only entity that hasn't demanded his help, Eternity.  Even though Doc defeats Eternity's champion and gains knowledge of what is occurring with the Infinity Crusade, Eternity erases the knowledge.

results.title: And Now...Centaurion
results.description: Kyllian is getting bored at Doc's mansion so he goes out for a stroll.  Meanwhile the immortal enemy of the gods Kyllian serve, Bellona, sends Centaurion to defeat him.

results.title: World Enough, And Time...
results.description: Dormammu is so afraid of The Goddess that he tries to convince Doc to allow himself to be used as Dormammu's conduit to this dimension.

results.title: Sword and Staff
results.description: Kyllian and Centaurion trade blows and the newcomer seems to able to hold his own(with the help of the Celtic Trio).

results.title: Blood Relations
results.description: Wong (controlled by Doc's Astral spirit) puts on the old Amulet of Agamotto and purple Cloak of Levitation and does battle with Baron Blood II.

results.title: Stand-Off
results.description: Bellona retrieves the defeated Centaurion, and Kyllian figures out that the benefits of having three Celtic gods inside you sometimes has a few hidden costs as well.

results.title: And a World Dies!
results.description: Urthona helps Jarakk defeat Pura-Shamutra (a god fighting on the side of the Trinity of Ashes) so that he can obtain a device to rebuild his world.  Meanwhile Kyllian is getting into more trouble.

results.title: Urthona Engaged
results.description: Doc battles Urthona over the death of Pura-Shamutra(it caused the cosmic ripple Doc felt last issue).  Meanwhile back on Earth, Kyllian gets sucked throught the Trivet and meets a Babe in the woods.

results.title: Cage of Refuge
results.description: Doc uses Kyllian's staff to locate Iskelior's pocket dimension.  As the dimensional barriers start to fall to Lilith, Doc has Kyllian seal himself into the Iskelior dimension.

results.title: Introducing: the Dread Daughter of Mephisto [The Faust Gambit Part II]
Demonic Re-possession [The Faust Gambit Part II]
results.description: Baron Mordo had promised a soul to both Satannish and Mephisto, so Doc has to deal with them, Mephista and the Sons of Satannish until he is forced to enter Agamotto's realm.

results.title: The Book of The Vishanti
results.description: Sara Krowler marries Nikolai Mordo at the request of her father, Viscount Heinrich Krowler, so that the resultant child can be used in a spell of Transferance to increase his own power.

results.title: Scatter...and Sister Nil [Siege of Darkness, Part 7]
results.description: Doc and the Midnight Son's are besieged at Doc's Sanctum.  When Doc tries to freeze time, Lilith interferes and splits him into three entities.  Sister Nil kills Imei and Doc has to destroy his own Sanctum!

results.title: Sacrifice Sorcerer Supreme
results.description: Doc and all his magical artifacts disappear when he gives the Sorcerer Supreme title back to Salom‚.  Then Strange appears and blasts Salom‚ with her own Elemental magick.

results.title: Stranger and Stranger
results.description: When the Oculus is found, Doctor Doom and Strange fight over its ownership.  Morbius' search for the real Doctor Strange finally hits paydirt.

results.title: Is There a Doctor in the House?
Song of the Blood Opal
results.description: Dr. Vincent Stephens has another party at The Tempo building, Doctor Strange kicks Morbius out of his new Sanctum, and Strange records the song of the Whole Moon Hawk.

results.title: Strangers Among Us: Act I of IV
The Brilliant One [Strangers Among Us, Act 1]
results.description: Strange searches for the next piece of Earth Magic, the Corel Crab, in the cave of The Brilliant One a Leviathan near Namor's Aquaria.  On land, Salom‚ gives us a brief glimpse of her new servant, Wong!

results.title: No More Namor! The Sub-Mariner [Strangers Among Us: Act II of IV]
Amok! [Strangers Among Us - Act 2]
results.description: Strange battles a Salom‚ possessed Namor (who recovers his Coral Crab).  Vengeance and Strange have a short battle while Wong and his partially resurrected Imei go looking for 'the other' Doctor Strange.

results.title: He's back, right? WONG! [Strangers Among Us: Act III of IV]
Shattered [Strangers Among Us - Act 3]
results.description: Wong and Imei(Xaos) kidnap Vincent Stevens and bring him to Salom‚. The Midnight Sons visit Doc and accuse him of practically everything that has ever gone wrong, as he tries to prepares for battle with Salom‚.

results.title: The Heart of Saturday Night
results.description: Clea returns to our dimension to elicit the aid of Doctor Strange, but finds that neither the Doctor nor his house are anywhere to be found.

results.title: Stranger at My Heels
results.description: Strange continues to try and convince Stevens to merge with him.

results.title: X-Factor's Polaris and Forge..at odds with Doctor Strange
Be With Me
results.description: After Vincent Stevens rejects Strange's appeal to merge, he searches for another and finds Polaris.

results.title: My Caterpillar -- My Enemy [The Faust Gambit Part III]
Agamotto Monamour [Faust Gambit Part III]
results.description: Doc and Agamotto talk, then battle, then talk some more.  Doc leaves to find out that Satannish and Mephisto are about to do battle at full size over New York. Agamotto takes an eye from Silver Dagger and restores Dr. Strange's right eye, along with all his talismans and his house.

results.title: TBOTV: The Mordo Chronicles, Part II
results.description: Dr. Strange and Morganna Blessing in cameo, battle Dormammu in 1943; Baron Mordo sacrifices his grandfather and mother to Dormammu.

results.title: Half Lives 1
results.description: Vincent Stevens uses Techno-Magick to possess the Hulk.

results.title: Half Lives 2 - Bodyslam
results.description: When Rick Jones finally helps force Vincent Stevens out of the Hulk, the Strangers agree to merge at the Tempo.  Doctor Strange gets attacked in his Forge, and Salom‚ gets a visit from the Vishanti.

results.title: Last Rites - First Verse [Last Rites]
results.description: Doc prepares for the final battle with Salom‚.  After an inner struggle to just give up, he fully embraces the Gaian Aura and dons the Aetheric Armor and wields the Aetheric Sword.

results.title: Threshold of Ashes [Last Rites, Second Verse]
results.description: Doc struggles to reacquire his energy from the Strangers. Clea nearly signs a truce with Dormammu in the Dark Dimension, and Salom‚ searches in vain for Doc at his Otherworldly Sanctum.

results.title: Mask and Mirror [Last Rites, Third Verse]
results.description: Salom‚ finally discovers Doc's Forge Canal, and the Strangers and Doc continue to battle for control over each other.

results.title: A Moment of Silence [Last Rites, Final Verse]
results.description: Doc finally defeats Strange but instead of absorbing him he sends him to merge with Nobel to help Clea in the Dark Dimension.  Doc fights Salom‚ and tricks her into reclaiming her Elemental fire and wins the fight.
